abstract: Cheyenne Woods, Cristie Kerr and P K Kongkraphan share first-round lead at Manulife LPGA Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.
lead_paragraph: Cheyenne Woods, Cristie Kerr and P. K. Kongkraphan matched the course record at nine-under-par 63 to share the first-round lead in the Manulife L.P.G.A. Classic.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Golf; Three-Way Tie in Ontario

snippet: Cheyenne Woods, Cristie Kerr and P. K. Kongkraphan matched the course record at nine-under-par 63 to share the first-round lead in the Manulife L.P.G.A. Classic.
